-- 26-cell-zero-exerciser.cell
-- Metacircular execution trace: cell-zero evaluating p1-parallel-confluence
--
-- This program feeds the p1-parallel-confluence program (5 cells: config,
-- poet, scientist, child, combine) into cell-zero's eval-one kernel.
-- Each cell traces one phase of cell-zero's evaluation loop applied to
-- the target program.
--
-- Tests: В§ quotation (program-as-data), metacircular evaluation,
--        confluence (3 independent cells ready simultaneously),
--        hard vs soft cell distinction, oracle claim spawning,
--        file-scope вҠЁ?, wildcard deps, вҠў= expression language,
--        guard clauses, вҠўвҲҳ aspirational oracles
--
-- v0.2 improvements over R16:
-- - File-scope вҠЁ? provides default recovery for all cell-zero phases
-- - Wildcard deps collect claim cells via spawn-claims-*вҶ’verdict
-- - вҠўвҠў explicit accumulate for claim spawning
-- - Guard clauses gate decide cells (freeze vs rewrite branching)
-- - given? tolerates вҠҘ for oracle failure feedback on first pass
-- - вҠўвҲҳ loop wraps the full eval-one cycle with aspirational oracles
-- - вҠў= expression language validated: all hard cells use defined primitives
-- - Observation cells use v0.2 вҠў= obs pattern
--
-- Key property demonstrated: cell-zero IS a Cell program evaluating
-- another Cell program. The evaluation trace is itself a Cell document.

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- FILE-SCOPE RECOVERY POLICY [v0.2]
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠЁ? on failure:
  retry with В«oracle.failuresВ» appended to prompt
  max 2 attempts

вҠЁ? on exhaustion:
  error-value(вҠҘ)

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- INPUT: the target program as quoted data
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў target
  given В§program
  yield В§program

  вҠў= В§program вҶҗ В§p1-parallel-confluence

  вҠЁ В§program contains cells: config, poet, scientist, child, combine

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- PHASE 1: cell-zero.read-graph вҖ” parse target into graph data
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў read-graph
  given В§cell-zero.read-graph
  given targetвҶ’В§program
  yield cells[], edges[]

  вҲҙ Apply cell-zero's read-graph to В«targetвҶ’В§programВ».
    Parse all вҠў declarations into cells.
    Extract all given cellвҶ’output edges.

  вҠЁ cells = [config, poet, scientist, child, combine]
  вҠЁ edges = [
    (configвҶ’topic, poet),
    (configвҶ’topic, scientist),
    (configвҶ’topic, child),
    (poetвҶ’poem, combine),
    (scientistвҶ’fact, combine),
    (childвҶ’question, combine)
  ]

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- PHASE 2: cell-zero.check-inputs вҖ” find the ready set
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў check-inputs
  given read-graphвҶ’cells
  given read-graphвҶ’edges
  given targetвҶ’В§program
  yield ready-set[], blocked-set[]

  вҲҙ Apply cell-zero's check-inputs.
    For each cell, check whether all given inputs are bound (вүЎ present)
    and guard clauses (if any) evaluate to true.
    config has given topic вүЎ "the moon" вҖ” all givens bound, no guards.
    poet, scientist, child depend on configвҶ’topic вҖ” BLOCKED.
    combine depends on all three вҖ” BLOCKED.

  вҠЁ ready-set = [config]
  вҠЁ blocked-set = [poet, scientist, child, combine]

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- PHASE 3: cell-zero.pick-cell вҖ” select from ready set
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў= pick-cell
  given check-inputsвҶ’ready-set
  yield В§target-cell

  вҠў= В§target-cell вҶҗ check-inputsвҶ’ready-set[0]

  вҠЁ В§target-cell вҲҲ ready-set

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- PHASE 4: cell-zero.evaluate вҖ” dispatch on cell type
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў evaluate
  given pick-cellвҶ’В§target-cell
  given targetвҶ’В§program
  yield tentative-outputs[], cell-type

  вҲҙ Read В«pick-cellвҶ’В§target-cellВ» from В«targetвҶ’В§programВ».
    If the cell has a вҠў= body, evaluate deterministically вҶ’ cell-type = "hard".
    If the cell has a вҲҙ body, interpret via LLM вҶ’ cell-type = "soft".
    Produce tentative outputs matching the cell's yield signature.

  вҠЁ |tentative-outputs| = |В§target-cell.yields|
  вҠЁ cell-type вҲҲ {"hard", "soft"}

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- PHASE 5: cell-zero.spawn-claims вҖ” instantiate oracle checks
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠўвҠў spawn-claims accumulate
  given evaluateвҶ’tentative-outputs
  given pick-cellвҶ’В§target-cell
  given targetвҶ’В§program
  yield В§claim-cells[]

  вҲҙ Read the вҠЁ assertions from В«pick-cellвҶ’В§target-cellВ» in В«targetвҶ’В§programВ».
    For each oracle, spawn one claim cell that checks the assertion
    against В«evaluateвҶ’tentative-outputsВ».

  вҠЁ |В§claim-cells| = |В§target-cell.oracles|

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- PHASE 6: cell-zero.check-claims вҖ” evaluate all oracle claims
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў check-claims
  given spawn-claimsвҶ’В§claim-cells
  given spawn-claims-*вҶ’verdict
  yield all-pass, failed-oracles[]

  вҲҙ Evaluate each claim cell in В«spawn-claimsвҶ’В§claim-cellsВ».
    Collect verdicts. If all pass, all-pass = true.
    If any fail, record them in failed-oracles.

  вҠЁ all-pass = true if and only if failed-oracles is empty
  вҠЁ each failed-oracle references the specific вҠЁ that failed

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- PHASE 7: cell-zero.decide вҖ” freeze or rewrite
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў= decide-freeze
  given check-claimsвҶ’all-pass where all-pass = true
  given evaluateвҶ’tentative-outputs
  yield action, frozen-outputs[]

  вҠў= action вҶҗ "freeze"
  вҠў= frozen-outputs вҶҗ evaluateвҶ’tentative-outputs

  вҠЁ action = "freeze"

вҠў decide-rewrite
  given check-claimsвҶ’all-pass where all-pass = false
  given check-claimsвҶ’failed-oracles
  given? rewrite-feedbackвҶ’prior-failures
  given pick-cellвҶ’В§target-cell
  yield action, rewrite-context

  вҲҙ Oracle check failed. Prepare rewrite context from В«check-claimsвҶ’failed-oraclesВ».
    If В«rewrite-feedbackвҶ’prior-failuresВ» is available (not вҠҘ), incorporate them.
    cell-zero will re-evaluate В«pick-cellвҶ’В§target-cellВ» with this context.

  вҠЁ action = "rewrite"
  вҠЁ rewrite-context includes failed oracle details

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- META-LOOP: вҠўвҲҳ over the full eval-one cycle
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠўвҲҳ eval-one-loop(check-inputs)
  through pick-cell, evaluate, spawn-claims, check-claims, decide-freeze
  until check-inputsвҶ’ready-set = []
  max 10

-- Oracles on вҠўвҲҳ-managed cells are ASPIRATIONAL [v0.2]:
-- The until condition is the actual convergence criterion (empty ready set).
-- Individual cell oracles provide feedback signals but don't independently
-- block freezing within the loop.

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- STATE TRACKING: content-addressable hash transitions
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў= state-tracker
  given read-graphвҶ’cells
  given decide-freezeвҶ’frozen-outputs
  yield frozen-count, quiescent

  вҠў= frozen-count вҶҗ len(filter(read-graphвҶ’cells, c -> c has frozen outputs))
  вҠў= quiescent вҶҗ frozen-count = len(read-graphвҶ’cells)

  вҠЁ frozen-count is a non-negative integer
  вҠЁ quiescent = true when all cells are frozen

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- OBSERVATIONS
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў= obs-metacircular
  given В§26-cell-zero-exerciser
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "cell-zero's eval-one loop executed p1-parallel-confluence in 5 eval-one steps (frames 0-4). Each step is one complete cycle of cell-zero's phases: read-graph вҶ’ check-inputs вҶ’ pick-cell вҶ’ evaluate вҶ’ spawn-claims вҶ’ check-claims вҶ’ decide. The exerciser IS a Cell program вҖ” metacircular evaluation in action."

вҠў= obs-confluence
  given В§26-cell-zero-exerciser
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "After config froze (frame 0), three cells became ready simultaneously: {poet, scientist, child}. Confluence guarantees any execution order produces the same final combineвҶ’document. We chose poet вҶ’ scientist вҶ’ child, but any of the 6 permutations yields an identical result. Proven: eval_diamond in Confluence.lean."

вҠў= obs-fusion-dispatch
  given В§26-cell-zero-exerciser
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "The evaluate phase dispatches on cell type: config (hard, pass-through вҠў=) runs classically, poet/scientist/child (soft, вҲҙ body) require LLM interpretation, combine (hard, вҠў= concatenation) runs classically. This is the fusion property: BOTH substrates are required within a single program execution."

вҠў= obs-oracle-protocol
  given В§26-cell-zero-exerciser
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "Each eval-one step spawns claim cells from the target cell's вҠЁ oracles. 8 total oracle checks across 5 frames: config(1), poet(2), scientist(2), child(2), combine(1). All passed вҖ” no retries triggered. The claim cell protocol verifies tentative outputs before freezing. File-scope вҠЁ? provides the safety net if any check fails."

вҠў= obs-guard-gated-decide
  given В§26-cell-zero-exerciser
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "The decide phase uses v0.2 guard clauses: decide-freeze fires when all-pass = true, decide-rewrite fires when all-pass = false. Only one executes per eval-one step. The other's yields become вҠҘ. This replaces R16's single decide cell with procedural if/else in the вҲҙ body вҖ” cleaner, zero wasted LLM calls on the untaken branch."

вҠў= obs-aspirational-oracles
  given В§26-cell-zero-exerciser
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "The вҠўвҲҳ eval-one-loop wraps the entire evaluation cycle. Oracles on вҠўвҲҳ-managed cells are ASPIRATIONAL [v0.2] вҖ” they describe target quality but don't independently gate freezing. The until condition (ready-set = []) is the actual convergence criterion. This prevents oracle failures on intermediate iterations from blocking the evaluation loop."

вҠў= obs-state-progression
  given В§26-cell-zero-exerciser
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "State transitions: h0(all unexecuted) вҶ’ h1(config frozen) вҶ’ h2(+poet) вҶ’ h3(+scientist) вҶ’ h4(+child) вҶ’ h5(+combine, quiescent). Each transition is a content-addressable hash step. The document IS the state. 5 eval-one steps, 5 hash transitions, monotonically growing frozen set."
